# Email Marketing Standards

## Compliance Requirements
- Implement explicit consent collection for marketing emails
- Store consent records with timestamp and source
- Apply regional compliance variations (GDPR, CAN-SPAM, CASL, etc.)
- Maintain audit trails of consent changes
- Implement preference and subscription management
- Honor unsubscribe requests within timeframes required by law

## Content Guidelines
- Apply consistent branding across all email communications
- Implement mobile-responsive design for all templates
- Use accessible design and content practices
- Follow subject line best practices for deliverability
- Include required legal footers and disclosures
- Maintain proper text-to-image ratios

## Email List Management
- Implement proper list segmentation strategies
- Apply regular list cleaning procedures
- Use double opt-in for new subscriptions
- Document list growth and management practices
- Implement proper handling of bounces and complaints
- Apply engagement-based sending frequency

